Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.10,0:01:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.38,0:01:37.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\fad(300,600)}{\fs40}名為α的野獸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.48,0:01:40.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…莫非是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.62,0:01:47.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.65,0:02:23.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回家 萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.31,0:02:28.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣擅自行動可不好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.79,0:02:31.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就知道你會來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.12,0:02:34.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好久不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.02,0:02:37.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉拉·琉特魯公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.28,0:02:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是長大了不少啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:42.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露西爾·艾利斯君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.53,0:02:46.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他現在還不到可以看「門」的階段
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.24,0:02:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是由你來決定的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.87,0:02:55.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您果然是個阻礙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:02:59.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你猜這個是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.42,0:03:01.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者遺物嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.37,0:03:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種東西可是殺不了我的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.76,0:03:05.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.06,0:03:06.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.11,0:03:14.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉碎吧 神獸滅絕
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.19,0:03:27.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次見面之前
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.79,0:03:31.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要找到可以殺死你的咒語才行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.96,0:03:44.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露西爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.80,0:03:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.35,0:03:48.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉特魯公爵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:50.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.76,0:03:53.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不像你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.19,0:03:54.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼沒殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.00,0:04:00.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那口氣 倒是越來越像樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.66,0:04:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉拉·琉特魯公爵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.24,0:04:07.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將那侵蝕羅蘭德的該死亡靈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.32,0:04:08.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找出來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.64,0:04:10.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.33,0:04:12.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.70,0:04:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我不知不覺中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.67,0:04:17.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界似乎起了巨大的變化
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:21.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是我理想中的王者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:24.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切遵照您的指示
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.85,0:04:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.71,0:04:48.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了拯救…這腐朽的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.89,0:04:51.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天叫你來不為別的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.26,0:04:55.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是想知道你的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:58.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我不滿意你的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.83,0:05:00.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.65,0:05:04.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就聽聽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.15,0:05:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問吧 露西爾·艾利斯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.76,0:05:09.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就知道你會這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.80,0:05:11.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.85,0:05:22.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再駐足不前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.06,0:05:34.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阻擋在眼前的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.24,0:05:37.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是誰都殺無赦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.22,0:05:42.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為此我什麼都能接受
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.37,0:05:48.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使是惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.93,0:05:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直 一直在等待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.06,0:05:59.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來吧 成為吾主
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.89,0:06:01.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拋棄一切
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.44,0:06:03.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將一切獻作祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.79,0:06:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為吾劍之主吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:10.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你將是吞噬 開拓這世界的…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.17,0:06:11.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.48,0:06:20.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 拯救世界吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.45,0:06:21.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.65,0:06:25.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你為所欲為
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.92,0:06:33.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會讓你為所欲為
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.82,0:06:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即將消失的假貨還能有合作為
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.22,0:06:39.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡說八道 你才是假貨
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.96,0:06:42.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.54,0:06:45.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你會輸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:51.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不認為那笨蛋輕易就會死…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:57.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.14,0:07:03.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟有美麗的小姐跟我搭話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.43,0:07:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真幸運
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.19,0:07:12.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子 到底對萊納做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.45,0:07:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.39,0:07:18.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜歡萊納嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.90,0:07:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:23.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.98,0:07:25.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.66,0:07:27.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:31.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺有一套嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.64,0:07:35.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還真想多看看你的真本領
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.74,0:07:37.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道你有什麼目的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.05,0:07:40.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但若敢小看我 小心沒命
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.15,0:07:42.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰會沒命？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.20,0:07:43.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.68,0:07:54.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重量大概三倍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.74,0:07:58.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別想了 你沒有勝算的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.88,0:08:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 你問我對萊納做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.48,0:08:05.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.01,0:08:08.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用小刀插進他的心臟殺了他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:12.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他血流如注 表情甚是可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我沒說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.89,0:08:18.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納死了 你明白了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.01,0:08:28.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀 惹哭你了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.08,0:08:31.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.70,0:08:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:35.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要…殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.39,0:08:48.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合格
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.36,0:08:50.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉這麼欺負你
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.60,0:08:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如此重視萊納…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.14,0:08:58.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:24.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.64,0:09:26.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起源（α）即破壞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.06,0:09:29.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾不行創造
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.15,0:09:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行惠澤
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.31,0:09:31.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.52,0:09:32.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,僅行消除
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.02,0:09:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回歸純白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.13,0:09:39.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一天吾等了好久
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.88,0:10:00.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟以為這種仿冒品就能封住吾等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.04,0:10:03.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一切都結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.56,0:10:06.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞噬了你 便能解除這封印吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.70,0:10:10.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吾將前往「α」 一切遵照契約
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.81,0:10:13.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧 解開所有公式者
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.74,0:10:22.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人體實驗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.34,0:10:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.58,0:10:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有報告說其發狂後從實驗設施逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.65,0:10:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個破忌者　因為被施過禁忌之術
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.43,0:10:35.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲得了超越常人的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:39.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺 殺
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.87,0:10:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 阿斯塔爾陛下即位以來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.01,0:10:47.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人體實驗應該被禁止了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.00,0:10:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是羅蘭德帝國破忌者追擊部隊隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.62,0:10:54.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蜜爾可·卡拉德中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.37,0:10:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你習得了羅蘭德魔法…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.91,0:11:00.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.28,0:11:08.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託 聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.37,0:11:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上頭有令 那個破忌者殺無赦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.16,0:11:33.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下知道這件事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.01,0:11:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是 因為人體實驗是陛下的指令
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.36,0:11:42.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下他…正常嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.96,0:11:45.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 無比正常
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.75,0:11:49.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因為有必要才重新開始這種實驗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.58,0:11:53.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都知道這件事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.76,0:12:00.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…盧克你們一直瞞著我的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.93,0:12:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅蘭德的黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.66,0:12:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以…解脫了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.99,0:12:13.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了…就能解脫了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.89,0:12:18.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.35,0:12:20.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以活著長大
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.85,0:12:23.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會和我結婚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.79,0:12:29.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果倖存下來 能和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.94,0:12:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間到 過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.61,0:12:37.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.12,0:12:40.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算約定…也沒有意義啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.92,0:12:43.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我是要死的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:44.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.32,0:12:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊 太愛哭
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.27,0:12:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要說什麼要死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:52.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你能行的啦 這麼頑強
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.19,0:12:55.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒打算死呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.49,0:12:58.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:04.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 你也別死
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.37,0:13:06.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.35,0:13:09.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.96,0:13:14.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒能救你 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.25,0:13:19.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能這樣做 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.69,0:13:25.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使接下來即將發生一切
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.93,0:13:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在陛下的劇本之中
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.49,0:13:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:36.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所生存的國度 我一定會守護到底
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.95,0:13:49.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 阿特法爾嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:53.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種程度的詛咒就想壓制我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.62,0:14:00.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.02,0:14:02.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快 萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.45,0:14:17.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…誰
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.35,0:14:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你長得…這麼大了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.80,0:14:30.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琉拉 是你給了我時間吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.23,0:14:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在等你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.81,0:14:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只為了見你 一直在等待
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.22,0:14:39.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了…見我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.74,0:14:42.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我愛你 萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.41,0:14:51.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.10,0:14:56.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在「編造所有公式者」出現之前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:57.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快往深處去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.06,0:14:59.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後去觸碰「門」
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.70,0:15:00.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,門？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:05.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了守護你珍重的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.73,0:15:08.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區一個祭品 大膽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.27,0:15:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大膽大膽大膽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.98,0:15:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想再多碰碰你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.11,0:15:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再多說幾聲我愛你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.36,0:15:23.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想一直陪在你身邊 看著你成長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.56,0:15:36.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡…可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.13,0:15:39.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底要我做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.72,0:15:41.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,休想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.19,0:15:44.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要在此成為吾之祭品
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:12.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救…救…我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.15,0:16:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要…將你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.95,0:16:23.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想…吃了你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.85,0:16:34.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.22,0:16:35.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我記得是突然被奇怪的傢伙捅了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.41,0:16:45.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.20,0:16:49.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…早
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.00,0:16:56.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.80,0:17:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混賬萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光是逃避的你 無法拯救萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.75,0:17:08.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.49,0:17:11.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以拯救世界為借口
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.03,0:17:13.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你出賣了萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.99,0:17:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.97,0:17:16.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要閉嘴的是你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.48,0:17:17.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和你不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.98,0:17:19.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納不會放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.13,0:17:22.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別滿口空想
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.99,0:17:25.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避選擇 逃避恐懼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.43,0:17:28.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避痛苦的你救不了萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.39,0:17:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我選擇了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.02,0:17:32.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選擇向前進
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.80,0:17:34.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不讓你得逞
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.24,0:17:37.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你就從黑暗中拯救萊納看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.35,0:17:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你做不到的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.00,0:17:42.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你做得到 我早就做了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.72,0:17:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此 我還是要救萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.32,0:17:52.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:53.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.43,0:17:56.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會殺了萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.55,0:17:59.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他陷入黑暗之前救他出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:02.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只要睡著就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.38,0:18:06.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會終結一切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.63,0:18:28.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 到底誰贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.85,0:18:35.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決定了吧 要怎麼處置萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.12,0:18:52.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 你也不記得發生了什麼事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:57.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 好像有人告訴了我什麼很重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.72,0:19:02.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.94,0:19:11.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是啥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.02,0:19:31.43,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}忘れてたあの日の面影が
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.02,0:19:31.43,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}那一天已忘却的面容
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.88,0:19:37.39,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}空の向こう 微かに
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.88,0:19:37.39,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}在天空彼方隐隐浮现
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.01,0:19:45.47,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}心なら繋がっていたはず
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.01,0:19:45.47,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}心灵原本应早已相通
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:52.95,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}震えた瞳は応えずに
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.00,0:19:52.95,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}颤抖的瞳眸却无回应
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.14,0:19:56.23,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}どんなに信じても
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.14,0:19:56.23,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}如何相信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:19:59.68,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}どんなに伝えたくても
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.31,0:19:59.68,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}如何呐喊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:05.98,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}この声は届かない
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:05.98,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}这声音你已无法听到
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.67,0:20:10.77,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}光のフィルメント
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.67,0:20:10.77,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}光之Fillment
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:15.63,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}全てをこの身体に刻み
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.86,0:20:15.63,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}一一铭刻于此身
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:20.74,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}歩き出す ここから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.11,0:20:20.74,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}就从此地 迈出步伐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.84,0:20:24.42,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}記憶のセグメント
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.84,0:20:24.42,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}记忆的Segment
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:29.76,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}今絡まる運命の糸解き
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.56,0:20:29.76,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}解开此刻交缠的命运丝线
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.10,0:20:33.64,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}強くなりたい
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.10,0:20:33.64,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}变得坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.74,0:20:36.68,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}また出逢えたら
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.74,0:20:36.68,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}若能再重逢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.76,0:20:46.25,opjp,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}もっと守れるように 君を
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.76,0:20:46.25,opcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\fad(300,300)}{\blur2)}定能守护你 更多
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.14,0:20:55.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解開所有公式者…是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.05,0:21:00.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你竟然查到這麼多了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.70,0:21:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是我看中的人 果然優秀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.98,0:21:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.00,0:21:08.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在羅蘭德發生了什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.36,0:21:09.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有其真正意義
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.57,0:21:14.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會這麼拚命 是為了萊納·琉特嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.10,0:21:21.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了拯救世界而奮戰不休的勇者
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.13,0:21:24.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,崩潰以後追求力量 最終被封印起來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.47,0:21:28.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而為了解除這封印
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.32,0:21:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吞噬了害怕寂寞的惡魔之力量
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.03,0:21:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害怕寂寞的惡魔…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.02,0:21:46.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.35,0:21:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加斯塔克很快就將進攻中央大陸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.82,0:21:53.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該會和羅蘭德正面衝突吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.74,0:21:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前 我要借你之手救出萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.58,0:22:00.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在席恩·阿斯塔爾背叛萊納之前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.24,0:22:02.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.48,0:22:04.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩怎麼會背叛萊納
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.63,0:22:07.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,墮落的黑暗勇者為了拯救世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.91,0:22:10.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將吞噬害怕寂寞的惡魔
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.45,0:22:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在比死更殘酷的絕望 吞噬萊納·琉特之前
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.19,0:22:18.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要把他救出來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.04,0:22:21.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從墮落的黑暗勇者手中救出來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.69,0:22:26.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要帶著萊納回來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.66,0:22:29.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.03,0:22:41.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,單戀真痛苦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.10,0:22:44.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下 一切準備就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.61,0:22:47.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.50,0:22:48.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時機到來了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.38,0:22:52.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要向未來前進
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.12,0:22:55.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓不再有淚水的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.74,0:22:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為現實
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.71,0:23:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加斯塔克萬歲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.17,0:23:08.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前進
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.11,0:23:19.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萊納…
